7 SECTION 3. There is appropriated out of the general
8 revenues of the State of Hawaii the sum of $871,016 or so much
9 thereof as may be necessary for fiscal year 2025-2026 and
10 $1,841,016 or so much thereof as may be necessary for fiscal
11 year 2026-2027 for a permanent safe spaces for youth program
12 within the office of youth services.
13 The sums appropriated shall be expended by the department
14 of human services for the purposes of this Act.
15 SECTION 4. New statutory material is underscored.
16 SECTION 5. This Act shall take effect on July 1, 2025.
